snippet.title: Eldritch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Eldritch is a first-person action game inspired by roguelikes, immersive sims, and H. P. Lovecraft. Available now for Windows PC from David Pittman and Minor Key Games. Coming soon to Mac and Linux.

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/252630
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/eldritch
itch.io: https://minorkeygames.itch.io/eldritch
Direct: http://eldritchgame.com/#buy

http://www.eldritchgame.com
http://www.minorkeygames.com
https://www.twitter.com/dphrygian

Music: "Requiem for a fish" by The Freak Fandango Orchestra.
http://www.freakfandango.es/
